cations of the tidal modes can be more\nsignificative than expected and that the time of tidal synchronization strongly\ndepends on the values of the rheological parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2019 17:26:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2019 17:52:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2020 12:39:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 14:55:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-16"}
