itive parameterization\nof $u_0(\\lambda_0)$, we demonstrate this concept by using model atmospheres to\ncalculate the brightness distribution for $\\nu$ Ophiuchi and predict\n$\\theta_{\\rm UD, 0}(\\lambda_0)$, and then comparing the predictions to\ncoherently averaged data from observations taken with the NPOI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2019 18:04:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-26"}
