endent polymer drag.\nAdditionally, we observe transient flow-induced intermolecular hooks in the\nstartup of flow which lead to diverse and unique stretching pathways.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jul 2019 03:34:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-23"}
